data.description: Welcome to this completely move in ready home! This property was remodeled in 2022. This open concept floor plan features 3 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, private laundry area and a very spacious eat in kitchen. Brand new carpet, flooring, lighting, cabinets and fixtures are featured through out the home. All appliances are included with the home. On the exterior you will find a spacious front yard and backyard. This home also has a 1 car detached garage and ample extra parking. The seller is offering possession at closing! Don't miss out on this opportunity to find your new home before the holiday's!
